ygData.messageBody:
Hello all
I am new to this email list as this is my 1st gnome
I, as have all of you checked all the web sites and made the basics,
lanterns, bait, compass, cams etc...i have done nothing as i am sure all u
have but pump money into the skill and into supplies. We all know that much
of what we make is useless, Lets hope this will change I have made only 4
points in the skill and it has cost me considerable money, but I am holding
onto th notion that many of the BETTER items can be produced given time and
levels and a cooperative spirit that we share information.
Lets keep at it
Dwizz Singez mage 24
Tribunal server
